### [choco://intel-killer-performance-suite](choco://intel-killer-performance-suite)
To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [(unofficial) choco:// Protocol support ](https://chocolatey.org/packages/choco-protocol-support)

---

The Intel Killer™ Performance Suite package installs the Windows 10 and Windows 11 Wi-Fi, Ethernet drivers, and Killer Networking Software.

### Notes:

* Some drivers from this package may not have been updated and are the same as the previous package.
* Only Windows 10 and Windows 11 64-bit Operating systems are supported.
 
**[PACKAGE NOTES](https://github.com/bcurran3/ChocolateyPackages/blob/master/intel-killer-performance-suite/readme.md)**
